# Monochrome Bento Box Animations Update

The Bento Box previews in `LandingFeatures.tsx` have been fully refactored to align with the new minimalist Black & White design system. We stripped away all rainbow/accent colored hues in favor of sleek, high-contrast monochrome styles.

## Changes Made

### 1. Updated PRD (`landing-content.md`)
- 📝 **Aesthetics & Design System Added**: We instituted the strict 'monochrome aesthetic' rule inside `docs/landing-content.md` under the Synchronization Protocol, explicitly detailing that rainbow gradients are no longer allowed and accent colors must be reserved only for external CTAs.

### 2. AIAgentPreview (Chat Animation)
- Refactored the user message bubble from `bg-primary` to a sharp inverted `bg-foreground text-background`.
- Replaced the typing bubbles to use `bg-foreground/40` and `bg-foreground/5` rather than tinting them with primary.
- In the dynamically animated chart, updated the CTR / CVR bars to grayscale representations (`bg-foreground/80` and `bg-foreground/30`).
- Transformed the "Distinct Action Plan" widget. It now prominently utilizes neutral backgrounds and foreground borders rather than the standard blue aesthetic. "CheckCircle" icons and badges now use stark inverse `bg-foreground text-background` styling instead of green.

### 3. DeepResearchPreview (Live Scanner)
- Replaced the primary text colors on the active "Search" input area to `text-foreground`.
- Transformed the "Scanning..." progress bar animations and the pulsing status icon to `bg-foreground`.
- Stripped the "Verified" and "20% Rebill" text of their green font colors in favor of structural high contrast (`text-foreground`). The checkmark chip is now a clean `bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-900 border-border` container.

### 4. AnalyticsPreview (Dashboard Mock)
- **KPI Metrics:** Translated the Copy Profit (green), Notion Comm (blue), and Avg Cpa (amber) digits completely into bold `text-foreground` elements.
- **ROI Badge:** Shifted the "+40% ROI" indicator out of green borders to a crisp `border-border bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800` layout.
- **SVG Chart:** The animated Area Chart stroke & gradient drops now source directly from `var(--foreground)` rather than the `primary` color variable, providing a sleek greyscale look across both light and dark themes.

### 5. ProjectManagementPreview
- Altered the core "Active" states connecting modules to use inversion (`bg-foreground text-background`) rather than cycling through blue or green styling.
- Extracted the primary coloring from the "Saving..." CTA modals, replacing them entirely with `bg-foreground`.
- The "Project" metadata tag structure has been shifted to high contrast layout formats.

## Testing & Validation
- **Lint Check:** Executed `npx eslint "src/containers/landing/LandingFeatures.tsx"` successfully to confirm absolute cleanliness in the structural react syntax. No execution issues found.
